batch.user_prompt_template:
generate exactly one sentence for typing practice in Korean.
- Topic: {topic}
- Tone/Style: {style}
- Number inclusion constraint: {number_condition}
- Length constraint: Exactly around {target_len} Korean characters (excluding spaces and punctuation marks), with a tolerance of ±10 characters.
- Requirement: {complex_sentence}
- Warning: {no_newlines} Output strictly in a single line.
- Warning: {allowed_punctuation}

subject.user_prompt_template:
Generate exactly 20 sentences for typing practice in Korean.
- Topic: "{subject}"
- Length constraint: Each sentence should have exactly around 80 Korean characters (excluding spaces and punctuation marks), with a tolerance of ±20 characters.
- Number inclusion constraint: {number_condition}
- Requirement: {complex_sentence}
- Warning: {no_newlines} Output strictly in a single line per sentence.
- Warning: {allowed_punctuation}
